{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":336,"text":"Motor racing is a funny old business."},{"time":2593,"text":"We make a new car every year,"},{"time":4910,"text":"and then we spend the rest of the season"},{"time":7098,"text":"trying to understand\nwhat it is we've built"},{"time":9874,"text":"to make it better, to make it faster."},{"time":13095,"text":"And then the next year, we start again."},{"time":16370,"text":"Now, the car you see in front\nof you is quite complicated."},{"time":20608,"text":"The chassis is made\nup of about 11,000 components,"},{"time":24227,"text":"the engine another 6,000,"},{"time":26695,"text":"the electronics\nabout eight and a half thousand."},{"time":29788,"text":"So there's about 25,000 things\nthere that can go wrong."},{"time":34189,"text":"So motor racing is very much\nabout attention to detail."},{"time":39015,"text":"The other thing about Formula\n1 in particular"},{"time":42278,"text":"is we're always changing the car."},{"time":44402,"text":"We're always trying to make it faster."},{"time":46682,"text":"So every two weeks, we will be making"},{"time":49666,"text":"about 5,000 new components\nto fit to the car."},{"time":53866,"text":"Five to 10 percent of the race car"},{"time":56044,"text":"will be different\nevery two weeks of the year."},{"time":59796,"text":"So how do we do that?"},{"time":62105,"text":"Well, we start our life\nwith the racing car."},{"time":65849,"text":"We have a lot of sensors\non the car to measure things."},{"time":69840,"text":"On the race car in front of you here"},{"time":71722,"text":"there are about 120 sensors\nwhen it goes into a race."},{"time":74881,"text":"It's measuring all sorts\nof things around the car."},{"time":78533,"text":"That data is logged. We're logging about"},{"time":80585,"text":"500 different parameters\nwithin the data systems,"},{"time":84289,"text":"about 13,000 health parameters and events"},{"time":87954,"text":"to say when things are not\nworking the way they should do,"},{"time":92519,"text":"and we're sending that data\nback to the garage"},{"time":95344,"text":"using telemetry at a rate\nof two to four megabits per second."},{"time":100323,"text":"So during a two-hour race,\neach car will be sending"},{"time":103450,"text":"750 million numbers."},{"time":105725,"text":"That's twice as many numbers\nas words that each of us"},{"time":108868,"text":"speaks in a lifetime."},{"time":110499,"text":"It's a huge amount of data."},{"time":113117,"text":"But it's not enough just\nto have data and measure it."},{"time":115762,"text":"You need to be able to do\nsomething with it."},{"time":117920,"text":"So we've spent a lot of time and effort"},{"time":120314,"text":"in turning the data into stories"},{"time":122183,"text":"to be able to tell,\nwhat's the state of the engine,"},{"time":125288,"text":"how are the tires degrading,"},{"time":127560,"text":"what's the situation\nwith fuel consumption?"},{"time":131308,"text":"So all of this is taking data"},{"time":134096,"text":"and turning it into knowledge\nthat we can act upon."},{"time":137898,"text":"Okay, so let's have a look\nat a little bit of data."},{"time":140536,"text":"Let's pick a bit of data from"},{"time":142566,"text":"another three-month-old patient."},{"time":145645,"text":"This is a child, and what you're\nseeing here is real data,"},{"time":149816,"text":"and on the far right-hand side,"},{"time":151793,"text":"where everything starts getting\na little bit catastrophic,"},{"time":154579,"text":"that is the patient going\ninto cardiac arrest."},{"time":157964,"text":"It was deemed to be\nan unpredictable event."},{"time":161196,"text":"This was a heart attack\nthat no one could see coming."},{"time":164985,"text":"But when we look at the information there,"},{"time":167535,"text":"we can see that things\nare starting to become"},{"time":169884,"text":"a little fuzzy about five minutes\nor so before the cardiac arrest."},{"time":173913,"text":"We can see small changes"},{"time":175950,"text":"in things like the heart rate moving."},{"time":178333,"text":"These were all undetected\nby normal thresholds"},{"time":180819,"text":"which would be applied to data."},{"time":183227,"text":"So the question is, why\ncouldn't we see it?"},{"time":186370,"text":"Was this a predictable event?"},{"time":188951,"text":"Can we look more\nat the patterns in the data"},{"time":191961,"text":"to be able to do things better?"},{"time":195341,"text":"So this is a child,"},{"time":197991,"text":"about the same age\nas the racing car on stage,"},{"time":201223,"text":"three months old."},{"time":202853,"text":"It's a patient with a heart problem."},{"time":205458,"text":"Now, when you look at some of the data\non the screen above,"},{"time":208926,"text":"things like heart rate, pulse,\noxygen, respiration rates,"},{"time":213828,"text":"they're all unusual for a normal child,"},{"time":216904,"text":"but they're quite normal\nfor the child there,"},{"time":219546,"text":"and so one of the challenges\nyou have in health care is,"},{"time":223684,"text":"how can I look at the patient\nin front of me,"},{"time":226535,"text":"have something which is specific for her,"},{"time":229582,"text":"and be able to detect when\nthings start to change,"},{"time":232370,"text":"when things start to deteriorate?"},{"time":234469,"text":"Because like a racing car, any patient,"},{"time":237519,"text":"when things start to go\nbad, you have a short time"},{"time":240495,"text":"to make a difference."},{"time":242326,"text":"So what we did is we took a data system"},{"time":245080,"text":"which we run every two weeks\nof the year in Formula 1"},{"time":248211,"text":"and we installed it\non the hospital computers"},{"time":251213,"text":"at Birmingham Children's Hospital."},{"time":253503,"text":"We streamed data\nfrom the bedside instruments"},{"time":255942,"text":"in their pediatric intensive care"},{"time":258499,"text":"so that we could both look\nat the data in real time"},{"time":261954,"text":"and, more importantly, to store the data"},{"time":264826,"text":"so that we could start to learn from it."},{"time":267883,"text":"And then, we applied an application on top"},{"time":272267,"text":"which would allow us to tease\nout the patterns in the data"},{"time":275537,"text":"in real time so we could\nsee what was happening,"},{"time":278493,"text":"so we could determine when\nthings started to change."},{"time":282206,"text":"Now, in motor racing, we're\nall a little bit ambitious,"},{"time":286069,"text":"audacious, a little bit\narrogant sometimes,"},{"time":288618,"text":"so we decided we would also\nlook at the children"},{"time":292016,"text":"as they were being transported\nto intensive care."},{"time":294973,"text":"Why should we wait\nuntil they arrived in the hospital"},{"time":297521,"text":"before we started to look?"},{"time":299121,"text":"And so we installed a real-time link"},{"time":302118,"text":"between the ambulance and the hospital,"},{"time":304954,"text":"just using normal 3G\ntelephony to send that data"},{"time":308730,"text":"so that the ambulance became an extra bed"},{"time":311217,"text":"in intensive care."},{"time":314353,"text":"And then we started looking at the data."},{"time":318055,"text":"So the wiggly lines\nat the top, all the colors,"},{"time":320976,"text":"this is the normal sort of data\nyou would see on a monitor --"},{"time":324170,"text":"heart rate, pulse,\noxygen within the blood,"},{"time":327942,"text":"and respiration."},{"time":330577,"text":"The lines on the bottom,\nthe blue and the red,"},{"time":333330,"text":"these are the interesting ones."},{"time":334831,"text":"The red line is showing\nan automated version"},{"time":337899,"text":"of the early warning score"},{"time":339496,"text":"that Birmingham Children's Hospital\nwere already running."},{"time":342235,"text":"They'd been running that since 2008,"},{"time":344321,"text":"and already have stopped cardiac arrests"},{"time":346577,"text":"and distress within the hospital."},{"time":349334,"text":"The blue line is an indication"},{"time":351766,"text":"of when patterns start to change,"},{"time":354266,"text":"and immediately, before we even started"},{"time":356575,"text":"putting in clinical interpretation,"},{"time":358283,"text":"we can see that the data\nis speaking to us."},{"time":361153,"text":"It's telling us that something\nis going wrong."},{"time":364689,"text":"The plot with the red and the green blobs,"},{"time":368505,"text":"this is plotting different components"},{"time":371310,"text":"of the data against each other."},{"time":373857,"text":"The green is us learning\nwhat is normal for that child."},{"time":377697,"text":"We call it the cloud of normality."},{"time":380307,"text":"And when things start to change,"},{"time":382548,"text":"when conditions start to deteriorate,"},{"time":385112,"text":"we move into the red line."},{"time":387350,"text":"There's no rocket science here."},{"time":389007,"text":"It is displaying data that exists\nalready in a different way,"},{"time":393120,"text":"to amplify it, to provide\ncues to the doctors,"},{"time":396511,"text":"to the nurses, so they can\nsee what's happening."},{"time":399249,"text":"In the same way that a good racing driver"},{"time":402379,"text":"relies on cues to decide\nwhen to apply the brakes,"},{"time":406423,"text":"when to turn into a corner,"},{"time":407899,"text":"we need to help\nour physicians and our nurses"},{"time":410817,"text":"to see when things\nare starting to go wrong."},{"time":414437,"text":"So we have a very ambitious program."},{"time":417383,"text":"We think that the race is on to do\nsomething differently."},{"time":422119,"text":"We are thinking big.\nIt's the right thing to do."},{"time":425023,"text":"We have an approach which,\nif it's successful,"},{"time":428435,"text":"there's no reason why it\nshould stay within a hospital."},{"time":431079,"text":"It can go beyond the walls."},{"time":432807,"text":"With wireless connectivity these days,"},{"time":434878,"text":"there is no reason why\npatients, doctors and nurses"},{"time":438322,"text":"always have to be in the same place"},{"time":440493,"text":"at the same time."},{"time":442486,"text":"And meanwhile, we'll take\nour little three-month-old baby,"},{"time":446481,"text":"keep taking it to the track,\nkeeping it safe,"},{"time":450238,"text":"and making it faster and better."},{"time":452571,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":453976,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}